gujarati.context:
Tough thorns will break, that's how it will be; 
This life is necessary to go, now it will have to go; 
There is no room for giving in the home, nor any living being escapes.

Here is the translation:

This said Shyam got settled, thieves came taking away the village; 
Kept a dark night in one house, thieves did not speak then there.
